    dc:creator "Tabell, Jukka; Junnilainen, Jari; Sihvonen, Pasi" ;
    dc:date "2024" ;
    dc:title "Eupithecia conquesta Tabell & Junnilainen, a new species from Cyprus (Lepidoptera, Geometridae, Larentiinae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/nl.47.114137.figures1-4>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/nl.47.114137.figures5-7>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/nl.47.114137.figures8-10> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/nl.47.114137.figures1-4>
    dc:description "Figures 1 - 4. Adults and labels of Eupithecia spp. 1, 2. E. conquesta sp. nov. 1. ♂ paratype. 2. ♀ paratype. 3. E. phoeniceata (Rambur), France. 4. E. oxycedrata (Rambur), Spain." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/962532" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/nl.47.114137.figures5-7>
    dc:description "Figures 5 - 7. Male genitalia and sternite A 8 of Eupithecia spp. 5. E. conquesta sp. nov., holotype, GP 6222 J. Tabell. Vesica photographed from paratype slide Sihvonen 2882. 6. E. phoeniceata (Rambur), France, Vidauban, 20. ix. 2006, GP 6223 J. Tabell. Vesica photographed from slide Sihvonen 2880 (France: Var, Vidauban, 6. x. 2005, coll. T. Ranki). 7. E. oxycedrata (Rambur), Spain, Mijas, 24. ix. 2012, GP 4 x 2012 J. Tabell. Vesica photographed from slide Sihvonen 2883 (Greece: Olympus, 750 m, 24. iv. 2006, coll. JUJ). Circle indicates the point of origin of ductus ejaculatorius. Vesica of each species photographed from ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/962533" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/nl.47.114137.figures8-10>
    dc:description "Figures 8 - 10. Female genitalia of Eupithecia spp. 8. E. conquesta sp. nov., paratype, GP 6236 J. Tabell. 9. E. phoeniceata (Rambur), France, La Ciotat, 24. x. 1963, GP 6226 J. Tabell. 10. E. oxycedrata (Rambur), Spain, Mijas, 24. ix. 2012, GP 6237 J. Tabell. Circle indicates the point of origin of the ductus seminalis." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/962534" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

